To programatically get the list, execute in the browser console:
 
 const i = [];
 document.querySelectorAll('*[id]').forEach((el) => { 
  if(el.textContent.match(/^(microsoft|Microsoft|Wandisco)/)) {
    i.push(el.textContent)
  }});
  i;
